Operand constraints.

<EnumerationList title="Enumeration values">

<Link id="aaa8eb58fd1b8466eb64a43df890cb8c1ae01b27a05209c02ca1bdb5a6033731fb" />
<EnumerationListItem name="TIED_TO">

</EnumerationListItem>

<Link id="aaa8eb58fd1b8466eb64a43df890cb8c1aa8498cb1d31308a367c23286fa443716" />
<EnumerationListItem name="EARLY_CLOBBER">

</EnumerationListItem>

</EnumerationList>

These are encoded in 16 bits with one of the low-order 3 bits specifying that a constraint is present and the corresponding high-order hex digit specifying the constraint value. This allows for a maximum of 3 constraints.
